message.text:
𝐔𝐦𝐚’𝐲 𝐤𝐚𝐲𝐨 𝐝𝐢𝐭𝐨𝐲 🔱𝐏𝐮𝐥𝐚𝐧𝐠 𝐊𝐨𝐧𝐬𝐞𝐡𝐨🔱!

Oo, tama ang narinig mo 📢 — ngayon ang 𝒉𝒖𝒍𝒊𝒏𝒈 𝒂𝒓𝒂𝒘 ng 𝗙𝗘𝗨-𝗥𝗖𝗬𝗖 𝗠𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿𝘀𝗵𝗶𝗽 𝗔𝗽𝗽𝗹𝗶𝗰𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 𝐚𝐭 𝐫𝐞𝐧𝐞𝐰𝐚𝐥, huwag papalampasin ang panibagong biag, bagong kabanata, at bagong kwento ng paglilingkod ang naghihintay sa’yo. 🎉

📌 Pumili lamang ng 𝗶𝘀𝗮𝗻𝗴 𝗸𝗼𝗺𝗶𝘁𝗲 na gusto mong salihan.

Huwag mag-alala, kahit isa lang ang mapili mo, 𝗽𝘄𝗲𝗱𝗲 𝗸𝗮 𝗽𝗮 𝗿𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗺𝗮𝗸𝗶𝘀𝗮𝗹𝗶 𝘀𝗮 𝗶𝗯𝗮𝗻𝗴 𝗺𝗴𝗮 𝗮𝗸𝘁𝗶𝗯𝗶𝗱𝗮𝗱 𝗻𝗴 𝗶𝗯𝗮'𝘁 𝗶𝗯𝗮𝗻𝗴 𝗸𝗼𝗺𝗶𝘁𝗲! 🥰

🔗𝐌𝐚𝐠-𝐀𝐩𝐩𝐥𝐲 𝐃𝐢𝐭𝐨: 
⁦https://forms.gle/S2tyqMkcG65TAENq6 ⁩

message.text:
𝐔𝐦𝐚’𝐲 𝐤𝐚𝐲𝐨 𝐝𝐢𝐭𝐨𝐲 🔱𝐏𝐮𝐥𝐚𝐧𝐠 𝐊𝐨𝐧𝐬𝐞𝐡𝐨🔱!

Oo, tama ang narinig mo 📢 — ngayon ang 𝒉𝒖𝒍𝒊𝒏𝒈 𝒂𝒓𝒂𝒘 ng 𝗙𝗘𝗨-𝗥𝗖𝗬𝗖 𝗠𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿𝘀𝗵𝗶𝗽 𝗔𝗽𝗽𝗹𝗶𝗰𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 𝐚𝐭 𝐫𝐞𝐧𝐞𝐰𝐚𝐥, huwag papalampasin ang panibagong biag, bagong kabanata, at bagong kwento ng paglilingkod ang naghihintay sa’yo. 🎉

📌 Pumili lamang ng 𝗶𝘀𝗮𝗻𝗴 𝗸𝗼𝗺𝗶𝘁𝗲 na gusto mong salihan.

Huwag mag-alala, kahit isa lang ang mapili mo, 𝗽𝘄𝗲𝗱𝗲 𝗸𝗮 𝗽𝗮 𝗿𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗺𝗮𝗸𝗶𝘀𝗮𝗹𝗶 𝘀𝗮 𝗶𝗯𝗮𝗻𝗴 𝗺𝗴𝗮 𝗮𝗸𝘁𝗶𝗯𝗶𝗱𝗮𝗱 𝗻𝗴 𝗶𝗯𝗮'𝘁 𝗶𝗯𝗮𝗻𝗴 𝗸𝗼𝗺𝗶𝘁𝗲! 🥰

message.text:
𝐔𝐦𝐚’𝐲 𝐤𝐚𝐲𝐨 𝐝𝐢𝐭𝐨𝐲 🔱𝐏𝐮𝐥𝐚𝐧𝐠 𝐊𝐨𝐧𝐬𝐞𝐡𝐨🔱!

Oo, tama ang narinig mo 📢 — ngayon ang 𝒉𝒖𝒍𝒊𝒏𝒈 𝒂𝒓𝒂𝒘 ng 𝗙𝗘𝗨-𝗥𝗖𝗬𝗖 𝗠𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿𝘀𝗵𝗶𝗽 𝗔𝗽𝗽𝗹𝗶𝗰𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 𝐚𝐭 𝐫𝐞𝐧𝐞𝐰𝐚𝐥, huwag papalampasin ang panibagong biag, bagong kabanata, at bagong kwento ng paglilingkod ang naghihintay sa’yo. 🎉

📌 Pumili lamang ng 𝗶𝘀𝗮𝗻𝗴 𝗸𝗼𝗺𝗶𝘁𝗲 na gusto mong salihan.

Huwag mag-alala, kahit isa lang ang mapili mo, 𝗽𝘄𝗲𝗱𝗲 𝗸𝗮 𝗽𝗮 𝗿𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗺𝗮𝗸𝗶𝘀𝗮𝗹𝗶 𝘀𝗮 𝗶𝗯𝗮𝗻𝗴 𝗺𝗴𝗮 𝗮𝗸𝘁𝗶𝗯𝗶𝗱𝗮𝗱 𝗻𝗴 𝗶𝗯𝗮'𝘁 𝗶𝗯𝗮𝗻𝗴 𝗸𝗼𝗺𝗶𝘁𝗲! 🥰

𝐔𝐦𝐚’𝐲 𝐤𝐚𝐲𝐨 𝐝𝐢𝐭𝐨𝐲 🔱𝐏𝐮𝐥𝐚𝐧𝐠 𝐊𝐨𝐧𝐬𝐞𝐡𝐨🔱!

Oo, tama ang narinig mo 📢 — ngayon ang 𝒉𝒖𝒍𝒊𝒏𝒈 𝒂𝒓𝒂𝒘 ng 𝗙𝗘𝗨-𝗥𝗖𝗬𝗖 𝗠𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿𝘀𝗵𝗶𝗽 𝗔𝗽𝗽𝗹𝗶𝗰𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 𝐚𝐭 𝐫𝐞𝐧𝐞𝐰𝐚𝐥, huwag papalampasin ang panibagong biag, bagong kabanata, at bagong kwento ng paglilingkod ang naghihintay sa’yo. 🎉

📌 Pumili lamang ng 𝗶𝘀𝗮𝗻𝗴 𝗸𝗼𝗺𝗶𝘁𝗲 na gusto mong salihan.

Huwag mag-alala, kahit isa lang ang mapili mo, 𝗽𝘄𝗲𝗱𝗲 𝗸𝗮 𝗽𝗮 𝗿𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗺𝗮𝗸𝗶𝘀𝗮𝗹𝗶 𝘀𝗮 𝗶𝗯𝗮𝗻𝗴 𝗺𝗴𝗮 𝗮𝗸𝘁𝗶𝗯𝗶𝗱𝗮𝗱 𝗻𝗴 𝗶𝗯𝗮'𝘁 𝗶𝗯𝗮𝗻𝗴 𝗸𝗼𝗺𝗶𝘁𝗲! 🥰

🔗𝐌𝐚𝐠-𝐀𝐩𝐩𝐥𝐲 𝐃𝐢𝐭𝐨:

message.text:
𝐀 𝐬𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐚𝐭 𝐥𝐢𝐠𝐡𝐭𝐬 𝐮𝐩 𝐞𝐯𝐞𝐫𝐲 𝐜𝐨𝐫𝐧𝐞𝐫. 𝐖𝐞𝐥𝐜𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐭𝐨 𝐁𝐚𝐜𝐨𝐥𝐨𝐝! 🎭

I am [Your Name], a proud [Your Program] student, carrying the vibrant colors, boundless joy, and resilient spirit that Bacolod is celebrated for.

Just like the Masskara Festival, I face challenges with courage, celebrate milestones with pride, and radiate smiles that inspire others.

𝐀𝐫𝐞 𝐲𝐨𝐮 𝐫𝐞𝐚𝐝𝐲 𝐭𝐨 𝐰𝐞𝐚𝐫 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐦𝐚𝐬𝐤 𝐨𝐟 𝐥𝐞𝐚𝐝𝐞𝐫𝐬𝐡𝐢𝐩, 𝐜𝐮𝐥𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐥𝐢𝐦𝐢𝐭𝐥𝐞𝐬𝐬 𝐩𝐨𝐭𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐢𝐚𝐥 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐮𝐬 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐁𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐒𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞 𝐨𝐟 𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌?

Join us this September 8–10, 2025 at the FEU Plaza and let’s celebrate unity, culture, and potential—together! 🎉

Hop in the DP Blast by clicking this link: 
https://twibbo.nz/ithmtamhunt2025

DP Frame by:Jilliane Lopez
Captin by: Bernadette Gaffud

#BidaSmileSaITHM
#TamHunt2025
#CultivatingLimitlessPotential
#ITHMStudentCouncil

message.text:
𝐀 𝐬𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐚𝐭 𝐥𝐢𝐠𝐡𝐭𝐬 𝐮𝐩 𝐞𝐯𝐞𝐫𝐲 𝐜𝐨𝐫𝐧𝐞𝐫. 𝐖𝐞𝐥𝐜𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐭𝐨 𝐁𝐚𝐜𝐨𝐥𝐨𝐝! 🎭

I am [Your Name], a proud [Your Program] student, carrying the vibrant colors, boundless joy, and resilient spirit that Bacolod is celebrated for.

Just like the Masskara Festival, I face challenges with courage, celebrate milestones with pride, and radiate smiles that inspire others.

𝐀𝐫𝐞 𝐲𝐨𝐮 𝐫𝐞𝐚𝐝𝐲 𝐭𝐨 𝐰𝐞𝐚𝐫 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐦𝐚𝐬𝐤 𝐨𝐟 𝐥𝐞𝐚𝐝𝐞𝐫𝐬𝐡𝐢𝐩, 𝐜𝐮𝐥𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐥𝐢𝐦𝐢𝐭𝐥𝐞𝐬𝐬 𝐩𝐨𝐭𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐢𝐚𝐥 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐮𝐬 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐁𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐒𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞 𝐨𝐟 𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌?

Join us this September 8–10, 2025 at the FEU Plaza and let’s celebrate unity, culture, and potential—together! 🎉

Hop in the DP Blast by clicking this link: 
https://twibbo.nz/ithmtamhunt2025

DP Frame by:Jilliane Lopez
Captin by: Bernadette Gaffud

#BidaSmileSaITHM
#TamHunt2025
#CultivatingLimitlessPotential
#ITHMStudentCouncil

message.text:
𝐀 𝐬𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐚𝐭 𝐥𝐢𝐠𝐡𝐭𝐬 𝐮𝐩 𝐞𝐯𝐞𝐫𝐲 𝐜𝐨𝐫𝐧𝐞𝐫. 𝐖𝐞𝐥𝐜𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐭𝐨 𝐁𝐚𝐜𝐨𝐥𝐨𝐝! 🎭

I am [Your Name], a proud [Your Program] student, carrying the vibrant colors, boundless joy, and resilient spirit that Bacolod is celebrated for.

Just like the Masskara Festival, I face challenges with courage, celebrate milestones with pride, and radiate smiles that inspire others.

𝐀𝐫𝐞 𝐲𝐨𝐮 𝐫𝐞𝐚𝐝𝐲 𝐭𝐨 𝐰𝐞𝐚𝐫 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐦𝐚𝐬𝐤 𝐨𝐟 𝐥𝐞𝐚𝐝𝐞𝐫𝐬𝐡𝐢𝐩, 𝐜𝐮𝐥𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞 𝐥𝐢𝐦𝐢𝐭𝐥𝐞𝐬𝐬 𝐩𝐨𝐭𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐢𝐚𝐥 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐮𝐬 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐁𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐒𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞 𝐨𝐟 𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌?

Join us this September 8–10, 2025 at the FEU Plaza and let’s celebrate unity, culture, and potential—together! 🎉

Hop in the DP Blast by clicking this link: 
https://twibbo.nz/ithmtamhunt2025

DP Frame by:Jilliane Lopez
Captin by: Bernadette Gaffud

#BidaSmileSaITHM
#TamHunt2025
#CultivatingLimitlessPotential
#ITHMStudentCouncil
